{"id":2940,"date":"2024-07-03T20:34:14","date_gmt":"2024-07-03T13:34:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2940"},"modified":"2024-07-03T20:34:40","modified_gmt":"2024-07-03T13:34:40","slug":"2940-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/2940-2\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P C\u00c1C NG\u00c0NH H\u1eccC \u201cHOT\u201d T\u1ea0I TDD"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 tr\u1ea3i qua 20 n\u0103m th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp, theo \u0111u\u1ed5i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian t\u00edch h\u1ee3p WILL (Work-Integrated Learning and Living), g\u1eafn k\u1ebft h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, h\u01b0\u1edbng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia, d\u1eabn d\u1eaft v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng theo nguy\u00ean l\u00fd \u201cTr\u00ed &#8211; N\u0103ng &#8211; Nh\u00e2n &#8211; H\u00f2a\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ngu\u1ed3n nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_22027\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22027\" style=\"width: 4400px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22027\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TDD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"4400\" height=\"2475\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-22027\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 v\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u201cTr\u00ed &#8211; N\u0103ng &#8211; Nh\u00e2n &#8211; Ho\u00e0\u201d<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o 13 ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc theo s\u00e1t nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt theo c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, tham quan t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf, c\u00f4ng ty, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong th\u1eddi gian <a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/truong-thanh-tu-giang-duong-doanh-nghiep\">H\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/a>. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea3 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1o cho sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh trang cho ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_22029\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22029\" style=\"width: 4170px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22029\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/SVTT3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"4170\" height=\"2163\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-22029\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sinh vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh trong Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>13 Ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4:<\/b><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><b>STT<\/b><\/td>\n<td><b>Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/b><\/td>\n<td><b>T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><b>Nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/cong-nghe-thong-tin\/chuong-trinh-ky-su-cntt\"><b>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Khoa h\u1ecdc d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o (x\u1eed l\u00fd \u1ea3nh)<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd<\/li>\n<li><span lang=\"VI\">K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u2013 (Agilead)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"3\">A00, A01, B00, D01<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/cong-nghe-ky-thuat-o-to\"><b>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u00d4 t\u00f4<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span lang=\"VI\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u00f4 t\u00f4<\/span><\/li>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ed1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/cong-nghe-ky-thuat-dien-dien-tu\"><b>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0110i\u1ec7n, \u0110i\u1ec7n t\u1eed<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 vi m\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n d\u1eabn<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><b>Nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/ke-toan\"><b>K\u1ebf to\u00e1n<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u1ebf to\u00e1n doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebf to\u00e1n &#8211; T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>A00, A01, B00, D01<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/quan-tri-kinh-doanh\/quan-tri-kinh-doanh\"><b>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh doanh<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span lang=\"VI\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb chu\u1ed7i cung \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 Logistics<\/span><\/li>\n<li>QTKD C\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng<\/li>\n<li>Digital Marketing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"3\">A00, A01, C00, D01<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/quan-tri-van-phong\"><b>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/b><\/a><b>\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh &#8211; V\u0103n th\u01b0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/luat\"><b>Lu\u1eadt<\/b><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><b>Nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/duoc-hoc\"><b>D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 kinh t\u1ebf d\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/li>\n<li>D\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>A00, A11, B00, D07<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><b>Nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh<\/b> <b>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef &#8211; Khoa h\u1ecdc x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/ngon-ngu-anh\"><b>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Anh<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ti\u1ebfng Anh du l\u1ecbch<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Anh &#8211; Trung<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>D01, D07, D14, D15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/quan-tri-khach-san\"><b>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/b><\/a><\/td>\n<td>A00, A01, C00, D01<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/nganh-dao-tao\/viet-nam-hoc-huon